	<div style="text-align:right;">
		LIMA, Daniel Renan Duarte Alves<sup>1</sup>; MICALI, Ana Carolina<sup>2</sup>; FARIA, Ana Cristina Ravazzani de Almeida<sup>3</sup>		<BR>
